-- Russia's Putin criticises NATO, Kiev 
-- 
-- Thu Dec 18, 2014 05:03AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Dec 18 (Reuters) - Russian President Vladimir Putin criticised NATO's eastward expansion following the fall of the Berlin Wall and said on Thursday Kiev was wrong to use armed forces against separatists in eastern Ukraine.

